Package timing

Class TimedRunnable

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Thread
timing.TimedRunnable
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Runnable
public class TimedRunnable
extends java.lang.Thread
implements java.lang.Runnable
Runs a specified Runnable, keeping track of when it started and ended, so that the Duration of the Runnable can be returned
